Part 8 - Box Model 

Box Model:

all the html elements are in the form of box model 

there are 5 things in box model: 

1. height 
2. width 
3. border 
4. padding
5. margin 

every content that is displayed in the webpage is considered as a box model
and this content have some height, width, padding, margin and border 

the space inside the border around the content is called padding
OR the space between the border and the content is called padding

the space outside the border of the content is called margin 
OR the space between the boxes is called margin 

